sentences: Patricia Elaine "Tricia" Baumhardt (n√©e Brock; born July 7, 1979) is an American contemporary Christian singer-songwriter raised in Dillsboro, Indiana.
In 2011, she released her first full-length, solo studio album The Road as Tricia Brock.
Her name was shortened to Tricia for her second album Radiate and its preview EP, Enough, in 2013.
